Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:52.42,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(436,1009)}On the path to immortality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:53.46,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(426,1010)}before a library of herbs and pills
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:00:54.90,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(417,1010)}there's far too much to take in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.18,0:00:56.62,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(425,1010)}Just who is singing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:00:57.74,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(430,1012)}who is hesitating
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:00:59.22,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(428,1009)}and who is standing atop the clouds?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:00.94,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(437,1010)}Out of the many who have come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:01.98,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(430,1009)}how many achieved the Way,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.10,0:01:03.10,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(432,1008)}rushing to a finish?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:05.06,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(426,1009)}Just who becomes anxious,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:07.90,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(429,1008)}and who is carefree?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:11.50,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(428,1010)}On the outside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:14.10,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(433,1009)}I pretend to be weak
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:15.70,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(433,1010)}You don't understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:18.18,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(429,1010)}hence you're confused
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.94,0:01:20.06,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(424,1010)}Just when, he asked,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:22.50,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(426,1009)}will I achieve completion?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:24.50,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(426,1009)}Could loneliness be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:27.38,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(421,1008)}the secret to immortality?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:31.26,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(425,1010)}Are mortals only allowed an ordinary life?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:32.78,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(430,1010)}I want to cultivate as an Immortal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:33.74,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(428,1010)}to remain young forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:34.90,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(425,1008)}My cultivation comes from hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:36.30,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(428,1010)}and not from luck
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.66,0:01:38.26,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(428,1008)}I didn't come here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:40.42,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(429,1013)}to sightsee
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:41.62,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(428,1010)}When I give it my all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:42.74,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(430,1009)}it'll surpass your imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:43.90,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(429,1010)}Even if the moon sleeps,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:44.90,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(429,1010)}I will endure until sunrise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:46.62,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(432,1010)}Why do I give my all?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:50.50,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(428,1010)}It's all to become eternal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:51.94,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(426,1009)}To prove that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:53.14,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(429,1010)}even as an ordinary mortal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:54.02,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(428,1008)}even when afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:01:55.34,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(432,1010)}shedding tears of fear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:56.18,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(433,1009)} I can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:57.02,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(429,1009)}break through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:01:59.58,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(429,1009)}to the clear sky beyond the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:00.82,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(429,1006)}Reshaping my mortal body
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:01.86,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(425,1009)}through countless rebirths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:02.62,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(428,1009)}until my primordial spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:03.90,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(429,1009)}manifests like a blaze
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.22,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(430,1010)}and finally
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.58,0:02:09.82,OP_EN1,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(484,1010)}harmonizing heaven and earth to become eternal
