Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior sister, were you worried about me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you died because of me, I'd feel indebted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You should feel honored to become part of Luochen Clan's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop spacing out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Escaping by yourself again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,let him turn us into fertilizer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.72,Default,X,0,0,0,,The show has just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's casting an illusory spell with the formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If we get entangled in fighting, we'll never escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior brother, Fireburst Pill!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that an illusion too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,finally showed itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you stand in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat dirt, mop head!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finally getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all your fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm stuck in this sick place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing the mop head
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,weakened the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Could she have been a part of the formation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,escaping comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior brother Hou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:05:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior brother Hou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,they confined him in this demonic tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,reduced to such a shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We found you at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Luochens have defected to Blood Stream Sect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But the formation is set.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nowhere to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Junior brother Bai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do me a favor
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as a sectmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,gotten the perfect opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You got lucky and survived Fallen Star Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you're staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,once I get back to the sect,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to avenge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If they stay in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the tear is going to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Feng Yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That sly bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:29.36,Default,L,0,0,0,,Trying to kill me by the hand of others?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Bai Xiaochun,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,will never...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,die in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,These pathetic vines 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,can't possibly trap me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a taste of the Fireburst Pill that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I prepared for Bai Xiaochun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.12,0:09:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm free?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Bai Xiaochun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm doomed to die today,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dragging you to my grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Be blown to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe he tried to blow me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank god for my Undying Skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Bai Xiaochun,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,emerged alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Bai Xiaochun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When I return to Spirit Stream Sect,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you into mincemeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid you'll never make it back to your...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stream
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because I'm useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If he hadn't tried to save me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,senior brother wouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He stopped the vines on his own
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and used a spell to push me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To think senior brother Feng
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,would be so loyal and righteous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unwise to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Chen Yue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me for being useless, Patriarch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I only managed to kill one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The other two saved the one we captured earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget your role and mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Great Spell of Spirit Reversal
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is only half a month away from completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After which, our clan will break free from the shackles of fate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and be bound by no limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,At this juncture,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we cannot afford any mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest assured, Patriarch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,will not leave Fallen Star Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.76,0:12:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This Jade Slip is a piece of crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't respond at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would know
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,even if we died in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we really make it out alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If they stay in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the tear is going to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Betraying our sect
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is punishable by death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way they will let us live.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior brother Feng died in there despite being
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,at the 7th level of Qi Condensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:12:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,even my unique message channel is unresponsive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wind Rider perished with senior brother Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,With such a long way ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,how can we avoid being hunted?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Life sure is tough
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for Bai Xiaochun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Junior brother Bai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You were always the most afraid of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But the more fear I feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the more I want to escape
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather fight it out than to be a sitting duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Us three
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.96,0:14:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,will return to the sect together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Junior sister Du.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Junior brother Bai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,After a short rest,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to regain some of my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Junior brother Bai,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think we'd reunite here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(970,70)}Oh, Senior brother Hou!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you made Xiaomei worry every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This punch is from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.12,Default,X,0,0,0,,Thanks for your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This was where I found
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,your Voice Transmission Jade Slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,what exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys must've taken the Wind Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and missed the villages around the Fallen Star Mountain Range.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,To break free from the Sect, the Luochen Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,set up Spiritual Restrictions
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and turned to the Blood Stream Sect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They even defied the Way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,killing innocents to harvest their breath of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever they went,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,not a soul was spared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual power all drained.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you guys haven't saved me in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've become a wronged ghost
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Spirit Reversal Formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wasted too much of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.44,0:15:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But your injury...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior sister...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You were so hasty to leave, dear friends from Spirit Stream Sect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't fulfilled my part as the host yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send you off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to seek revenge in your next life,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,remember: the man who killed you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is called Chen Yue.
